data.description: Welcome to your tranquil oasis nestled on 8.875 pristine wooded aces. This property not only offers the tranquility of nature but also comes with a host of valuable amenities. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area that features large windows, filling the room with abundant natural light. Step outside onto the the expansive porch, where you can savor the crisp, natural air. Now here's where this property truly stands out. Included with the home are all mounted televisions, two refrigerators and surround sound. The included lawn mower and ATV make property maintenance and exploration a breeze and allow you to fully embrace the outdoor lifestyle. But that's not all. This property is further enhanced by the inclusion of an above-ground swimming pool and all equipment. This is more than just a home; it's a lifestyle. Escape the city's hustle and bustle and come home to your haven, complete with all the amenities, to make your country livings dreams come true.
